<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَاظِرَةٌ}</span> ... تَرَى رَبَّهَا فِي الجَنَّةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَاسِرَةٌ}</span> ... عَابِسَةٌ، كَالِحَةٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَاقِرَةٌ}</span> ... مُصِيبَةٌ عَظِيمَةٌ تَقْصِمُ فَقَارَ الظَّهْرِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَلَّا}</span> ... حَقًّا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَلَغَتْ التَّرَاقِيَ}</span> ... وَصَلَتِ الرُّوحُ إِلَى أَعَالِي الصَّدْرِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَنْ رَاقٍ}</span> ... هَلْ مِنْ رَاقٍ يَرْقِيهِ، وَيَشْفِيهِ؟<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَظَنَّ}</span> ... أَيْقَنَ المُحْتَضِرُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْتَفَّتِ السَّاقُ بِالسَّاقِ}</span> ... اتَّصَلَتْ شِدَّةُ آخِرِ الدُّنْيَا بِشِدَّةِ أَوَّلِ الآخِرَةِ، وَالْتَفَّتْ إِحْدَى سَاقَيْهِ بِالأُخْرَى عِنْدَ المَوْتِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَسَاقُ}</span> ... سَوْقُ العِبَادِ لِلْجَزَاءِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَوَلَّى}</span> ... أَعْرَضَ عَنِ الإِيمَانِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَتَمَطَّى}</span> ... يَتَبَخْتَرُ فِي مِشْيَتِهِ مُخْتَالًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٣٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَوْلَى لَكَ فَأَوْلَى}</span> ... كَلِمَةُ وَعِيدٍ،<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> هَلَاكٌ لِكَ فَهَلَاكٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُدًى}</span> ... هَمَلًا لَا يُؤْمَرُ، وَلَا يُحَاسَبُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٣٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُمْنَى}</span> ... يُصَبُّ فِي الرَّحِمِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٣٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَقَةً}</span> ... قِطْعَةً مِنْ دَمٍ جَامِدٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٣٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَسَوَّى}</span> ... عَدَّلَ خَلْقَهُ، وَأَعْضَاءَهُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>